Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, want to play me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the man representing Japan in the next\NInternational Amateur Go Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuuhei is the top amateur player.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try thinking a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's playing quickly, but he is playing solidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. He may be a child, but he is a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:27.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He instantly read through my deciding\Nmove and responded correctly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:31.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's... incomparable to what he was like last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.46,Thinking,,0,0,0,,When did he change so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:37.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:39.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai! How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:45.39,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(320,115)}The Sixty-Third Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:45.40,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx330\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}I Won't Play Anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if there's\Na ghost in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's behind here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, here? But I didn't think\Nthere was anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know about this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn on the light now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.61,Background,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.11,Background,,0,0,0,,Books?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.08,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Kifu, Old Kifu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,These are old Kifu from back\Nwhen they were first printed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:53.21,Background,,0,0,0,,The oldest thing we have here\N is the Bouyuuseirakushuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:57.88,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fad(334,334)}Bouyuuseirakushuu is a collection of Kifu from the Northern Song\NDynasty of China (960~1170AD). The oldest match in the collection\Nis between two famous characters from a classical Chinese tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what you meant by\N"a room where I might find a ghost".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There weren't any ghosts here. Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.52,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Do you want to look at anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Shuusaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuusaku! Let's see... I think\N Shuusaku was from Kaei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:25.08,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fad(334,334)}Kaei (1844~1853) is part of Japanese history. It occurs in the latter\Nyears of the Edo period. A notable event of the period is the landing\Nof Commodore Perry in Uraga in the sixth year of Kaei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. I've never seen a Kifu\N played by Shuusaku before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never seen one before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even seen any of the\Nones that are still in print?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You should study old Kifu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll teach you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful. Those are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:50.19,bannersign,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\1c&H100900&\fscy50\blur0.8\frz50\pos(223,45)}SHUUSAKU KIFU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:50.27,bannersign,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\1c&H100900&\fscy50\blur0.8\frz50\pos(223,164)}SHUUSAKU KIFU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:50.39,bannersign,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\1c&H100900&\fscy50\blur0.8\frz50\pos(223,249)}SHUUSAKU KIFU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.48,bannersign,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\1c&H100900&\fscy50\blur0.8\frz50\pos(223,284)}SHUUSAKU KIFU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:50.19,bannersign,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H100900&\fscy80\blur0.8\frz57\pos(184,-43)}GO IN THE PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:50.27,bannersign,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H100900&\fscy80\blur0.8\frz57\pos(184,75)}GO IN THE PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:50.39,bannersign,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H100900&\fscy80\blur0.8\frz57\pos(184,161)}GO IN THE PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.48,bannersign,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H100900&\fscy80\blur0.8\frz57\pos(184,194)}GO IN THE PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.52,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll leave them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:52.60,Background,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now. Come get me when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home in half an hour.\N So don't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai... played these, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Torajirou let Sai play everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Take good care of those books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.54,Background,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:23.97,Background,,0,0,0,,I know the Sai from right now.\NWho cares about the old Sai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This move by Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an incredible move. It attacks\Nall of the surrounding sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,His opponent would lose all of his will\Nto fight after seeing a move like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.05,Background,,0,0,0,,Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have let him play more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.24,Background,,0,0,0,,That would have been much\Nbetter than my playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.74,Background,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I realize this before!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Touya would have been\Nmuch happier if Sai had played.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have let Sai, the genius, play everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Torajirou did...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike me, Torajirou was strong enough to\Ntry to become a pro when he met Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore he was able to see how strong Sai was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And he let Sai play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I... didn't know anything about Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had no idea how strong Sai was!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought about how I wanted to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When I finally realized how good Sai\Nwas... I still put myself ahead of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.35,Background,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have let Sai play...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,from the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone would agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been better to\Nlet Sai play all the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them! All of them! All of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to play! I won't ask to play again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,God! Please! Turn back time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn time back to when I first met him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The games are going to start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.95,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou... why aren't you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What is he doing? Did he oversleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And I thought that I would finally get\Na chance to watch you play today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Or... are you not coming!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:55.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya is bothered by Shindou's absence, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.41,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh no, the game is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.35,Background,,0,0,0,,About these four examples I gave...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:24.47,Background,,0,0,0,,They're all examples of conjugate modifiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:25.60,Background,,0,0,0,,Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,let's think about what the differences are between\Nthe conjugate modifiers in the following sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:32.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll let you play all the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,won't play anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll let you play all the games...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So come back... Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-Kun isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... and it's already time... let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou didn't come to the Ooteai this week either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If he is... He didn't bother telling anyone about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't come to Master Morishita's\Nstudy sessions either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:56.74,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fad(334,334)\pos(320,25)}The Fujiwara clan is a clan who dominated Japanese politics during much\Nof the Heian period (794~1185). Though Japan was ruled by the Imperial\Nfamily, and not by the Fujiwara clan, they had a great deal of control over\Nthe Emperors of the time by marrying females of the clan off to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:12:04.45,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fad(334,334)\pos(320,25)}The nature of their control over Japan changed at the end of the Heian period,\Nwhen they defeated the Taira clan in the Genpei conflict. For more information\Nabout the Fujiwara clan, take a class on Japanese history or literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai of the Fujiwara doesn't exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that look on your face? I researched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A noble who tutored the Emperor in Go during the Heian period, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I even called my teacher to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean!? What are you basing that on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... it is wrong of me to say that he didn't exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To be accurate, we don't know\Nwhether he existed or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means that he's not in any books or records.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You don't know if he existed or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai existed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:45.86,Background,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you talking to Mr. Matsui,\Nthe social studies teacher, about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I need one less handicap stone\Nagainst Kaneko-san now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Play me again when you have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.18,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you doing with your pro matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'm not playing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about!? Are\Nyou even listening to me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:38.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't go to Master Morishita's study sessions anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:42.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't go to Kawai-san's Go salon anymore, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:46.85,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:52.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to look towards me instead of Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:56.07,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Even though that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I... can't surpass Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.07,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wonder why he disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:30.34,Background,,0,0,0,,You're neater than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, he just doesn't have anything... at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you at least need a fridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya, what about laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan on doing laundry at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll probably eat at home\Nor eat at my teacher's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? How are you living on your own then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.79,Background,,0,0,0,,All I need is my Go board and stones for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I envy you. I want to live on my own, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free to come stay here anytime, Komiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you bring me food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunch of pros are going to come\Nhere on Saturdays, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pros? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:15.31,Background,,0,0,0,,Saeki-san, and Okada-san,\Nand Nakayama-san, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't shown up at the Institute\Nat all. I haven't told him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... Master Morishita was angry, and\Ntold me to forget about him. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Waya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That study session on Saturday...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go to it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't study with my teacher on Saturdays, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.33,Background,,0,0,0,,Of course! You should all come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda-kun and Komiya can because they're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel uncomfortable because I would\Nonly lower the level of discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you study if you worry\Nabout stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting at the preliminaries again\Nthis year for the pro exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Iijima-kun already quit being an Insei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm at my limit now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya, have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A few pros from the Kyuseikai went to China to\Nstudy and to promote international relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Isumi-kun went with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He did!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san is continuing Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... he is taking the pro exams again this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san's an outsider, so he'll begin at\Nthe preliminaries two months from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to be playing us again in the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san... in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-Kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... Has Shindou gone home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a different class...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou was in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaneko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go up those stairs, turn right on the second\Nfloor, and the library will be on your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru's at the library? What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. He was just staring into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Staring into space?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:55.93,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so unlike him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:24.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to him after...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.46,Thinking,,0,0,0,,the game against Master Touya on the Internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.25,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.39,Background,,0,0,0,,W-Wh-What is it,Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always appear so suddenly!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad for my heart! What are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come to the Wakajishisen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you going to your matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's a waste for someone like me to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.13,Background,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:30.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,because you see Sai inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't play anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't play!? You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:40.74,Background,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:45.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You're waiting for Sai, not me. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:50.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai has... disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:55.34,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I want to let you play him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you become a pro for!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why did you disappear, Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it to play me? Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:10.34,Background,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:12.26,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\c&HCDF8F8&\4c&H7CD26E&\shad2\bord0\pos(150,243)\fad(0,1250)}{\alpha&HFF&\t(0,32,\alpha&H00&)}U{\alpha&HFF&\t(32,64,\alpha&H00&)}m{\alpha&HFF&\t(64,96,\alpha&H00&)}e{\alpha&HFF&\t(96,128,\alpha&H00&)}z{\alpha&HFF&\t(128,160,\alpha&H00&)}a{\alpha&HFF&\t(160,192,\alpha&H00&)}w{\alpha&HFF&\t(192,224,\alpha&H00&)}a{\alpha&HFF&\t(224,256,\alpha&H00&)}Y{\alpha&HFF&\t(256,288,\alpha&H00&)}u{\alpha&HFF&\t(288,320,\alpha&H00&)}k{\alpha&HFF&\t(320,352,\alpha&H00&)}a{\alpha&HFF&\t(352,384,\alpha&H00&)}r{\alpha&HFF&\t(384,416,\alpha&H00&)}i{\alpha&HFF&\t(416,448,\alpha&H00&)}'{\alpha&HFF&\t(448,480,\alpha&H00&)}s
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, aren't the stars pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:18.41,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs22.5\3c&H117AF8&\4c&H117AF8&\fad(459,501)\bord1\shad0.5\pos(459,365)}Teacher Yukari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:18.41,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HF90000&\4c&HF90000&\fad(459,501)\bord1\shad0.5\pos(214,192)}Yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:18.41,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs22.5\3c&HF627EF&\4c&HF627EF&\fad(459,501)\bord1\shad0.5\pos(112,365)}Mai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, have you heard this story about Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,Background,,0,0,0,,There are 361 intersections on a 19x19 board.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:26.10,Background,,0,0,0,,This is the same as the number\Nof days in ancient China.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.52,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\3c&H126A14&\4c&H126A14&\fscy120\bord1\shad0.5\fad(417,417)\pos(320,303)}There are 361 intersections on a 19x19 board
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.52,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\3c&H1464C6&\4c&H1464C6&\bord1\shad0.5\fad(417,417)\pos(317,368)}There were 361 days in an old Chinese year
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:31.88,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\3c&H126A14&\4c&H126A14&\fad(459,459)\fscy115\bord1.5\shad0.5\pos(320,329)}There is a theory that one rotation around the first line is one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:32.03,Background,,0,0,0,,And it's said that one rotation around the\Nfirst line of the board represents a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.88,Background,,0,0,0,,And the white Go stones represent the Day,\Nand the black ones represent the Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:37.97,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs19\4c&HFFFFFF&\fscy115\bord1.5\shad0.5\fad(417,417)\pos(86,367)}White Stones\NRepresent Day   (Yang)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:37.97,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\an4\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1.5\shad0.5\fs19\fad(417,417)\fscy115\pos(370,367)}Black Stones\NRepresent Night (Ying)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:40.67,Background,,0,0,0,,In other words, the Go board shows\Nthe flow of time on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:44.32,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\3c&H0871F3&\4c&H0871F3&\fscy145\bord1.5\shad0.5\fad(459,501)\pos(211,368)}Go boards represent the flow of time on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:44.32,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\3c&HF60114&\4c&HF60114&\fscy145\fad(459,501)\bord1.5\shad0.5\pos(465,368)}and Go Stones represent the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:44.12,Background,,0,0,0,,and the Go stones... the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you picture when these\Ntwo are brought together?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Space?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:50.90,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs22.5\3c&HD90004&\4c&HD90004&\bord1\shad0.5\fad(542,375)\q2\fscx2000\t(0,542,1,\fscx100)\pos(322,349)}The Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a theory that Go boards and\Nstones were used for fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:54.93,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fscy115\3c&HB90003&\4c&HB90003&\bord1.5\shad0.5\fad(417,417)\pos(153,305)}There is a theory that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:54.93,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fscy115\bord1.5\shad0.5\3c&HB90003&\4c&HB90003&\fad(417,417)\pos(335,367)}Go Boards and Stones were once used for fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:57.37,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(542,0)\fs20.5\bord1.5\shad0.5\fscy115\3c&H1700E5&\4c&H1700E5&\pos(392,346)}To be Continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:01.11,Background,,0,0,0,,Don't touch the merchandise!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:04.69,Background,,0,0,0,,But this is Grandpa's!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.99,0:23:07.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Mister, you play Go? Want to play me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:12.66,Background,,0,0,0,,He has a 5-dan certificate! Don't\Nplay him in a game of Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:24.42,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:25.55,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
