Dialogue: 7,0:00:08.86,0:00:12.85,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}My heart walks, searching for something exciting
Dialogue: 8,0:00:12.66,0:00:16.31,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}that will passionately sway the beating in my chest.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:16.58,0:00:20.98,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}If I just wait for time to pass every day,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.96,0:00:22.90,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}nothing's going to change.
Dialogue: 11,0:00:24.38,0:00:28.37,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}I won't stop. I want to believe. I want to move forward.
Dialogue: 12,0:00:28.18,0:00:32.12,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}I will test my strength during my life.
Dialogue: 13,0:00:32.10,0:00:34.67,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}But even if I walk faster,
Dialogue: 14,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.50,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}I will definitely lose track of
Dialogue: 15,0:00:36.35,0:00:38.34,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}the important things.
Dialogue: 16,0:00:40.77,0:00:45.97,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}Tomorrow's wind will blow tomorrow,
Dialogue: 17,0:00:45.99,0:00:55.27,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}but I want to make the most out of this moment now.
Dialogue: 18,0:00:55.79,0:01:01.44,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}It's fantasy.  even if I'm wandering,
Dialogue: 19,0:01:01.58,0:01:05.49,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}even if I'm in a strange new world,
Dialogue: 20,0:01:05.42,0:01:07.32,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}I'll stand up to it,
Dialogue: 21,0:01:07.17,0:01:10.95,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}believing in myself more than anything else.
Dialogue: 22,0:01:11.26,0:01:17.00,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}It's destiny.  No matter where I am,
Dialogue: 23,0:01:17.06,0:01:20.92,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}I'm surrounded by the same sky,
Dialogue: 24,0:01:20.94,0:01:25.51,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,400)}so I'll be able to fly
Dialogue: 25,0:01:26.23,0:01:29.80,op61_english,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,900)}with my wings spread out.
